YOLOv11.model_description: YOLOv11 is a fast and accurate object detection model optimized for real-time applications.

YOLOv12.model_description: YOLOv12 improves upon YOLOv11 with enhanced accuracy and better handling of small objects.

SSD.model_description: SSD (Single Shot Detector) is a lightweight model designed for efficient object detection.

FasterRCNN.model_description: Faster R-CNN is a highly accurate object detection model suitable for complex tasks.

EfficientDet.model_description: EfficientDet is a scalable and efficient object detection model optimized for performance.

DETR.model_description: DETR (DEtection TRansformer) is a transformer-based model for end-to-end object detection.

RetinaNet.model_description: RetinaNet is a one-stage object detection model known for its focus on handling class imbalance.
